    "The cells are colored green if the accuracy difference w.r.t.",
    "the pre-trained model is positive and red if the difference is negative. formation.",
    "Furthermore, for both pre-trained and fine-tuned GPT-3.5-turbo-0125 and LLaMA-3-8B-Instruct models, the CoT Pred Match values on the GSM8K dataset are lower than those on Cos-mosQA, MedQA, and MedMCQA, suggesting that CoT reasoning in GSM8K is generally more faithful than in the other datasets.",
